{"tid":1844291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府宣布: 限制湖北省居民以及任何過去14日到過湖北省的人士進入香港!","createTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:18:10.000Z","uid":240448,"like":14,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"359721b323ac485f993702a942453006e186452b","tid":1844291,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdeeieS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdeeieS.png&h=7ddb815d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48e48845350bc228dfc2b5e20057f14dc9ae03a0","tid":1844291,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"面對咁顛既狗官，同埋黑警不停打壓支持防疫既人民，點樣先可以說服國際香港唔係疫埠呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHg8fGB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHg8fGB.png&h=077d795f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際戰線：求國際封鎖香港<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eNxNpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eNxNpS</a>"},{"pid":"43de381bec0319dad69f7ef6e8438879957e82d5","tid":1844291,"uid":52090,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，我要封關，全中国啊"},{"pid":"6901d5a0431c7b09479672257b76b46d332d6a0a","tid":1844291,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7ABcOV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7ABcOV7.jpg&h=0f21f561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鑑於中國肺炎疫症嚴峻，港共政府倒行逆施，徹底失去民意信任，已經無力領導現今疫症。<br />\n加上此疫症已經在香港鄰近地區面臨失控下，有機會令香港國家陷入危機，影響香港國家存亡。<br />\n<br />\n為防止中國肺炎在香港大規模爆發，在此宣佈，於香港時間2020年1月26日21時30分正式頒布緊急狀態令<br />\n為免錯過對抗中國肺炎黃金機會，全體連登網民會即時接管香港權力，全力帶領香港國民對抗中國肺炎，以 香港國民福祉為依歸。<br />\n請各位緊記，香港國家一切權力屬於人民，港共政權並非必然行使權力者。<br />\n<br />\n所有重大事件及決策，將會於連登討論區「政事台」討論及表決<br />\n議案帖文將會以【議案】為首以作識別<br />\n<br />\n大多數民意支持，以及正評數量淨值為1000或以上， 該議案會被視作「獲得通過」<br />\n<br />\n正式實現全民參政，全民議政<br />\n議案通過後，將運用全體公民力量及權力，以及民間一切可能的方法實行各種政策 。<br />\n請各位再次緊記，港共政權並非必然行使權力者，權力永遠歸於所有香港國民。<br />\n<br />\n【緊急狀態令】重大宣布：全體連登網民正式接管香港權力，全力領導香港對抗中國肺炎<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844124</a>"},{"pid":"7b5568cabb6792cd49e9b878b2df86d695371831","tid":1844291,"uid":240448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4524a7048a676fcd7955ff6bc3136731d76c453d","tid":1844291,"uid":52090,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"43de381bec0319dad69f7ef6e8438879957e82d5","tid":1844291,"uid":52090,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，我要封關，全中国啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">已負皮，我要全中国封關</span>"},{"pid":"6a2ac44a52fb1745cf69cf860d1b4f1063f7243a","tid":1844291,"uid":35667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"有乜撚用"},{"pid":"0f7fff699d6dfada9ca797124141cb2ec39f2c3c","tid":1844291,"uid":170395,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"封關啊屌"},{"pid":"59c262d1d5297b67db143284af04a6a1ca1d8097","tid":1844291,"uid":99172,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"點限制？又自願申報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class